[We have our whole lives ahead of us.
No need to rush.]

292
00:13:38,940 --> 00:13:40,380
How do you even have the time and mood

293
00:13:40,380 --> 00:13:41,180
to come here for tea?

294
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:43,500
We haven't

295
00:13:43,580 --> 00:13:45,420
sat down and chatted like this
in a long time.

296
00:13:46,740 --> 00:13:48,020
Let's just relax

297
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:49,140
and have some tea today.

298
00:13:50,700 --> 00:13:50,940
Yours.

299
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:53,220
So? Are you busy?

300
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:54,180
Not too bad.

301
00:13:56,580 --> 00:13:57,420
Haven't been here in a while.

302
00:13:57,700 --> 00:13:58,780
It's still so lively here.

303
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:00,540
Rui,

304
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:02,140
I heard

305
00:14:03,020 --> 00:14:04,020
you are

306
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:05,620
with Tan Siting now?

307
00:14:07,900 --> 00:14:08,100
Yes.

308
00:14:10,180 --> 00:14:10,540
Rui,

309
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:13,620
have you thought this through?

310
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:18,620
Did... Mom send you?

311
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:21,460
Dad, don't worry.

312
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:24,500
We've been through so much together.

313
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:28,020
We'll make it work.

314
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:31,500
And we're different from you and Mom.

315
00:14:32,660 --> 00:14:33,260
That's good.

316
00:14:34,580 --> 00:14:34,900
Have some tea.

317
00:14:36,340 --> 00:14:36,580
Dad,

318
00:14:37,340 --> 00:14:38,220
I've always wondered

319
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:42,340
how you and Mom have managed
these past few years.

320
00:14:45,580 --> 00:14:46,500
How else?

321
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:47,340
We just make do.

322
00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:48,380
Got used to it.

323
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:52,620
A lot of people ask me,

324
00:14:53,300 --> 00:14:54,140
"Feng Ming,

325
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:56,180
how did Gao Hui ever

326
00:14:56,660 --> 00:14:57,780
fall in love with you back then?"

327
00:14:59,460 --> 00:14:59,780
She said

328
00:15:00,380 --> 00:15:01,660
she liked my personality.

329
00:15:02,060 --> 00:15:02,940
She thought

330
00:15:03,540 --> 00:15:05,460
people who love reading are gentle.

331
00:15:06,260 --> 00:15:07,140
But look at things now.

332
00:15:07,780 --> 00:15:08,100
I

333
00:15:09,460 --> 00:15:10,020
haven't changed, have I?

334
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:11,420
But her?

335
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:12,900
She just doesn't like it anymore.

336
00:15:14,940 --> 00:15:15,540
So,

337
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:16,860
how long do you think

338
00:15:17,780 --> 00:15:18,660
feelings can really last?

339
00:15:19,340 --> 00:15:21,380
It was only after we got married
that we realized

340
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:24,140
life wasn't what we imagined.

341
00:15:25,180 --> 00:15:26,380
Even though I tried my best

342
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:27,740
to catch up with her perspective,

343
00:15:29,580 --> 00:15:30,420
some things

344
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:31,900
are just ingrained.

345
00:15:32,860 --> 00:15:33,260
They can't be changed.

346
00:15:34,180 --> 00:15:35,660
Like even now, I prefer

347
00:15:35,660 --> 00:15:37,140
open-air tea houses like this.

348
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:39,140
Down-to-earth.

349
00:15:39,660 --> 00:15:40,140
But your mom

350
00:15:41,060 --> 00:15:42,460
prefers high-end hotels.

351
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:44,660
Marriage

352
00:15:45,140 --> 00:15:45,900
is like a tree.

353
00:15:46,740 --> 00:15:47,620
If the roots aren't stable,

354
00:15:48,460 --> 00:15:49,700
it grows crooked

355
00:15:50,700 --> 00:15:51,140
and eventually

356
00:15:52,460 --> 00:15:53,260
falls.

357
00:15:57,020 --> 00:15:58,860
Have you noticed

358
00:15:58,980 --> 00:16:00,260
Ms. Wen acting a bit strange lately?

359
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:01,780
I noticed a while ago.

360
00:16:02,660 --> 00:16:04,780
Are she and Mr. Feng
having a disagreement?

361
00:16:05,660 --> 00:16:07,940
Mr. Feng hasn't come to pick her up
in a long time.

362
00:16:08,220 --> 00:16:10,060
I feel it's more serious
than just a disagreement.

363
00:16:11,220 --> 00:16:11,780
Really?

364
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:14,300
Do you think their wedding is still on?

365
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:15,900
Hard to say.

366
00:16:15,900 --> 00:16:16,540
Exactly.

367
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:19,220
Seeing her like that, it's hard to ask.

368
00:16:21,420 --> 00:16:22,180
Help me

369
00:16:22,180 --> 00:16:24,420
pull up the parent information
of the piano class students.

370
00:16:24,700 --> 00:16:25,060
Okay.

371
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:26,300
Look.

372
00:16:26,780 --> 00:16:26,980
This one.

373
00:16:27,060 --> 00:16:27,580
This one.

374
00:16:28,780 --> 00:16:29,340
Which one?

375
00:16:31,580 --> 00:16:32,020
Huang Hanfei.

376
00:16:32,020 --> 00:16:32,220
Yes.

377
00:16:32,740 --> 00:16:32,940
Okay.

378
00:16:33,940 --> 00:16:34,620
His mom came the other day

379
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:35,820
to inquire about his situation.

380
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:36,380
Right.

381
00:16:36,380 --> 00:16:37,340
He hasn't behaved lately.

382
00:16:38,300 --> 00:16:39,300
Just so you know,

383
00:16:39,740 --> 00:16:40,380
I'm not getting married.

384
00:16:40,940 --> 00:16:41,620
The wedding is off.

385
00:16:48,820 --> 00:16:49,300
Thank you.

386
00:16:49,340 --> 00:16:49,780
Thank you.

387
00:16:49,780 --> 00:16:50,180
No problem.

388
00:16:51,580 --> 00:16:51,940
Let's go.

389
00:16:53,540 --> 00:16:55,340
How's your dad doing?

390
00:16:56,260 --> 00:16:58,060
Better than I expected.

391
00:16:59,780 --> 00:17:00,380
That's good then.

392
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:02,620
You can finally put down

393
00:17:03,100 --> 00:17:04,420
that burden you've carried

394
00:17:04,820 --> 00:17:05,660
for so many years.

395
00:17:06,220 --> 00:17:06,540
Yeah.

396
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:07,340
And you?

397
00:17:09,340 --> 00:17:10,820
How's that boyfriend
you're so crazy about?

398
00:17:11,140 --> 00:17:11,740
Me?

399
00:17:12,100 --> 00:17:12,460
Yeah.

400
00:17:14,580 --> 00:17:15,180
He's great.

401
00:17:16,980 --> 00:17:17,820
In what way?

402
00:17:18,780 --> 00:17:20,620
Can we talk
about that kind of stuff out here?

403
00:17:20,780 --> 00:17:22,260
We'll save that for when we get home.

404
00:17:22,260 --> 00:17:23,820
Whisper it so no one else hears.

405
00:17:23,820 --> 00:17:24,380
How about

406
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:25,540
I tell you about his business?

407
00:17:27,420 --> 00:17:29,580
I'm telling you, his business is huge.

408
00:17:29,660 --> 00:17:30,260
But

409
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:31,260
it's mainly

410
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:32,660
in real estate.

411
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:35,380
Look.

412
00:17:35,580 --> 00:17:36,020
What?

413
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:39,260
A gift!

414
00:17:40,340 --> 00:17:41,380
A gift?

415
00:17:43,540 --> 00:17:46,380
"Wang Shuhan, Project Manager".

416
00:17:46,380 --> 00:17:47,420
Don't praise me yet.

417
00:17:48,100 --> 00:17:48,660
Let me tell you,

418
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:50,540
they started a new project

419
00:17:50,540 --> 00:17:51,460
in East District.

420
00:17:51,620 --> 00:17:52,420
But you know what?

421
00:17:52,420 --> 00:17:53,900
Old-school businessmen

422
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:55,780
have pretty old-fashioned thinking.

423
00:17:55,980 --> 00:17:56,380
So

424
00:17:56,380 --> 00:17:58,580
I suggested some newer ideas.

425
00:17:58,580 --> 00:17:59,820
They actually adopted them

426
00:17:59,820 --> 00:18:01,820
and gave me a Project Manager position.

427
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:03,900
- Excellent.
- Excellent.

428
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:08,180
Let's raise our coffees.

429
00:18:08,620 --> 00:18:09,860
To you

430
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:11,100
finding your dad,

431
00:18:11,580 --> 00:18:12,580
and to me

432
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:13,820
finding both a job

433
00:18:13,900 --> 00:18:14,580
and love.

434
00:18:15,100 --> 00:18:15,340
Cheers.

435
00:18:16,540 --> 00:18:17,060
You're head over heels.

436
00:18:17,980 --> 00:18:18,660
France?

437
00:18:18,660 --> 00:18:20,160
[Cygne]

438
00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:21,780
Are you going on your honeymoon?

439
00:18:24,900 --> 00:18:25,340
Look,

440
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:27,620
our vineyard

441
00:18:27,620 --> 00:18:29,060
has restored its production.

442
00:18:29,620 --> 00:18:31,380
The Cygne brand

443
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:32,460
is getting more and more recognition.

444
00:18:32,700 --> 00:18:33,900
I want to use this momentum

445
00:18:34,340 --> 00:18:36,340
to promote our brand in France.

446
00:18:37,460 --> 00:18:38,860
Through tastings

447
00:18:39,620 --> 00:18:40,380
and wine competitions there,

448
00:18:40,980 --> 00:18:41,540
we can truly

449
00:18:42,100 --> 00:18:43,060
expand our brand

450
00:18:43,820 --> 00:18:44,860
and establish ourselves

451
00:18:44,940 --> 00:18:45,860
in the international market.

452
00:18:46,740 --> 00:18:47,380
Sir,

453
00:18:47,700 --> 00:18:49,020
how long will you be gone?

454
00:18:49,580 --> 00:18:51,220
What about the business here?

455
00:18:51,460 --> 00:18:53,220
We still have
so many unfulfilled orders.

456
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:55,580
And so many manufacturers...

457
00:18:55,580 --> 00:18:56,380
I'm leaving it to you.

458
00:18:57,980 --> 00:18:58,380
We...

459
00:18:58,380 --> 00:18:59,100
Us?

460
00:18:59,740 --> 00:19:00,740
You'll be fine.

461
00:19:01,460 --> 00:19:02,380
Qi, your role stays the same.

462
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:03,660
You're responsible

463
00:19:04,140 --> 00:19:04,580
for orders

464
00:19:04,580 --> 00:19:05,300
and client relations.

465
00:19:05,620 --> 00:19:06,620
Your job doesn't change either.

466
00:19:07,300 --> 00:19:08,940
At most, you'll just go to the winery

467
00:19:09,340 --> 00:19:10,380
a few more times in my place

468
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:11,380
and work closely

469
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:12,540
with Duoji,

470
00:19:12,620 --> 00:19:13,300
keeping in good communication.

471
00:19:13,580 --> 00:19:14,220
That's all.

472
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:15,980
Let's try it for a while.

473
00:19:16,260 --> 00:19:16,900
If it works out,

474
00:19:17,140 --> 00:19:18,700
I'll hand the company over
to you completely.

475
00:19:22,260 --> 00:19:23,260
And if any issues come up,

476
00:19:23,780 --> 00:19:26,060
I can always communicate
with you from France.

477
00:19:27,860 --> 00:19:28,460
But

478
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:30,860
Cygne is your life's work.

479
00:19:31,660 --> 00:19:32,500
Yes.

480
00:19:32,740 --> 00:19:35,020
How could the two of us possibly
manage it...?

481
00:19:35,460 --> 00:19:36,620
You two

482
00:19:36,620 --> 00:19:37,780
are already really capable.

483
00:19:38,420 --> 00:19:38,860
Besides,

484
00:19:39,660 --> 00:19:40,580
aren't you two working together

485
00:19:40,660 --> 00:19:41,820
better and better?

486
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:46,060
Okay.

487
00:19:46,820 --> 00:19:47,340
We'll do our best.

488
00:19:47,580 --> 00:19:48,380
Yes, sir.

489
00:19:53,100 --> 00:19:54,620
There's one more thing
I want to tell you.

490
00:19:55,780 --> 00:19:57,020
What other big news?

491
00:19:58,580 --> 00:19:59,780
Feng Rui and I are back together.

492
00:20:02,340 --> 00:20:03,100
Back together?

493
00:20:04,940 --> 00:20:05,860
And you've reunited with your child too?

494
00:20:08,020 --> 00:20:09,020
Not yet.

495
00:20:10,180 --> 00:20:11,940
Still want to get mentally ready.

496
00:20:12,780 --> 00:20:14,300
I'm afraid Le

497
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:16,620
might not accept it so quickly.

498
00:20:17,780 --> 00:20:18,660
True.

499
00:20:19,260 --> 00:20:20,860
Le is still so young.

500
00:20:21,460 --> 00:20:22,660
You need to give him some time.

501
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:23,940
Forget Le,

502
00:20:24,300 --> 00:20:24,860
if it were me,

503
00:20:25,060 --> 00:20:26,620
if I suddenly found out I had a mom,

504
00:20:26,860 --> 00:20:28,100
I couldn't accept it either.

505
00:20:29,060 --> 00:20:29,380
Yeah.

506
00:20:29,700 --> 00:20:30,700
We'll take it slow.

507
00:20:30,860 --> 00:20:32,340
We'll figure things out as we go.

508
00:20:36,100 --> 00:20:36,620
Siting.

509
00:20:38,500 --> 00:20:39,860
I won't say much

510
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:41,660
about you and Feng Rui.

511
00:20:42,300 --> 00:20:44,100
As long as you're happy with it,
that's enough.

512
00:20:45,740 --> 00:20:48,100
But his mom

513
00:20:48,860 --> 00:20:49,540
is a tough one.

514
00:20:51,300 --> 00:20:52,780
I knew you'd say that.

515
00:20:54,540 --> 00:20:55,540
But his mom

516
00:20:55,540 --> 00:20:57,540
has been standing between us
for so many years.

517
00:20:59,140 --> 00:20:59,820
It's a really difficult problem.

518
00:21:01,100 --> 00:21:02,220
I've already figured it out.

519
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:04,100
I'm building a life with Feng Rui,

520
00:21:04,100 --> 00:21:04,980
not his mom.

521
00:21:06,380 --> 00:21:07,780
Besides, we've already decided.

522
00:21:08,580 --> 00:21:09,660
We're planning to go to France.

523
00:21:12,300 --> 00:21:13,940
That way, we can stay away from his mom

524
00:21:14,860 --> 00:21:15,580
and avoid conflicts.

525
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:16,380
That's good.

526
00:21:17,740 --> 00:21:18,780
You just got back,

527
00:21:18,780 --> 00:21:19,540
and you're leaving again?

528
00:21:22,340 --> 00:21:23,180
Just to avoid his mom?

529
00:21:24,700 --> 00:21:25,580
Not entirely.

530
00:21:27,220 --> 00:21:28,100
I just don't want
any more entanglements.

531
00:21:30,940 --> 00:21:32,260
But have you considered

532
00:21:33,780 --> 00:21:34,620
that Feng Rui and his mom

533
00:21:34,620 --> 00:21:36,380
are still bound by blood?

534
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:38,780
Blood is thicker than water.

535
00:21:39,020 --> 00:21:39,860
How can you be sure

536
00:21:39,860 --> 00:21:41,580
they won't have any contact
in the future?

537
00:21:41,860 --> 00:21:43,220
What if his mother causes more trouble?

538
00:21:44,060 --> 00:21:44,860
Of course I've thought about it.

539
00:21:46,620 --> 00:21:47,420
But Feng Rui told me

540
00:21:48,500 --> 00:21:49,300
he'll handle it.

541
00:21:54,300 --> 00:21:55,180
That's good then.

542
00:23:15,060 --> 00:23:15,660
I could

543
00:23:15,700 --> 00:23:18,140
hear you all chattering from far away.

544
00:23:18,780 --> 00:23:20,020
Look what I brought you.

545
00:23:20,300 --> 00:23:21,100
Who's this?

546
00:23:21,540 --> 00:23:21,780
Coffee.

547
00:23:22,500 --> 00:23:23,780
Were you taking Yufan

548
00:23:23,780 --> 00:23:24,900
for interviews again?

549
00:23:25,460 --> 00:23:26,100
Couldn't really refuse.

550
00:23:26,100 --> 00:23:27,220
Had no choice but to go.

551
00:23:27,380 --> 00:23:28,220
Just finished.

552
00:23:28,500 --> 00:23:29,020
While

553
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:31,100
we were being interviewed today,

554
00:23:31,220 --> 00:23:32,660
I got a call from Sanxiao.

555
00:23:33,060 --> 00:23:34,460
They invited me

556
00:23:34,500 --> 00:23:37,020
to share our teaching experience.

557
00:23:37,940 --> 00:23:38,460
Impressive.

558
00:23:38,500 --> 00:23:40,140
Sanxiao Ballet Club

559
00:23:40,140 --> 00:23:42,140
is ranked number one in the city.

560
00:23:42,700 --> 00:23:43,260
Exactly.

561
00:23:43,300 --> 00:23:44,100
Its members

562
00:23:44,100 --> 00:23:46,220
get directly into
the university-affiliated middle school.

563
00:23:46,500 --> 00:23:47,300
Rankings and actual ability

564
00:23:47,620 --> 00:23:48,540
are two different things.

565
00:23:48,780 --> 00:23:50,180
The students from the top-ranked school

566
00:23:50,220 --> 00:23:51,460
haven't won an international gold medal!

567
00:23:52,780 --> 00:23:53,940
Yufan really makes us proud.

568
00:23:54,060 --> 00:23:54,420
Yes.

569
00:23:54,620 --> 00:23:55,100
Indeed.

570
00:23:55,940 --> 00:23:56,700
So

571
00:23:57,220 --> 00:23:58,340
now it's all about the results.

572
00:23:58,620 --> 00:24:00,420
Only good results bring attention

573
00:24:00,620 --> 00:24:01,980
and a voice.

574
00:24:02,540 --> 00:24:03,540
That's true.

575
00:24:03,740 --> 00:24:04,620
It comes down to ability.

576
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:06,940
Ms. Tan.

577
00:24:07,740 --> 00:24:08,460
Have some coffee.

578
00:24:08,940 --> 00:24:09,380
Okay.

579
00:24:11,860 --> 00:24:12,540
You deserve

580
00:24:12,540 --> 00:24:13,420
part of the credit too.

581
00:24:13,780 --> 00:24:14,380
I think

582
00:24:14,540 --> 00:24:15,460
you should get involved too.

583
00:24:16,060 --> 00:24:17,620
Not me. I'm socially awkward.

584
00:24:18,140 --> 00:24:18,620
Socially awkward?

585
00:24:18,980 --> 00:24:19,260
Yeah.

586
00:24:19,300 --> 00:24:20,540
I'll leave everything else to you.

587
00:24:20,980 --> 00:24:21,460
Alright then.

