00:24:22,060 --> 00:24:22,940
I'll handle

589
00:24:23,300 --> 00:24:24,020
the social butterfly stuff.

590
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:27,300
By the way,

591
00:24:27,700 --> 00:24:28,540
no one's leaving

592
00:24:28,540 --> 00:24:29,140
after work tonight.

593
00:24:29,740 --> 00:24:31,660
We're going to that Yunnan restaurant
I mentioned.

594
00:24:32,300 --> 00:24:33,140
My treat.

595
00:24:33,500 --> 00:24:33,940
Ms. Guan.

596
00:24:34,540 --> 00:24:35,900
I can't make it tonight.

597
00:24:35,940 --> 00:24:36,900
I have something to do at home.

598
00:24:38,100 --> 00:24:39,220
Another time then. Just the two of us.

599
00:24:39,540 --> 00:24:39,820
Okay.

600
00:24:41,540 --> 00:24:42,460
Anything else?

601
00:24:43,260 --> 00:24:44,060
Mushrooms.

602
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:45,180
Feng Lexuan,

603
00:24:46,460 --> 00:24:48,020
why was your dad's wedding off?

604
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:50,180
How should I know about adult stuff?

605
00:24:50,740 --> 00:24:51,500
Then ask him.

606
00:24:51,700 --> 00:24:52,620
Why don't you ask him?

607
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:53,980
Why are you asking me?

608
00:24:54,660 --> 00:24:55,300
Feng Lexuan,

609
00:24:55,300 --> 00:24:56,740
so now you're not the one
giving me advice?

610
00:24:57,740 --> 00:24:59,340
I really don't know why.

611
00:25:00,980 --> 00:25:02,020
Because he fell out of love.

612
00:25:04,460 --> 00:25:06,020
Didn't know you had it in you,

613
00:25:06,740 --> 00:25:07,700
Yang Zihuan.

614
00:25:09,740 --> 00:25:10,500
I was just guessing.

615
00:25:11,140 --> 00:25:13,540
Could it be your dad
is still thinking about your mom?

616
00:25:14,540 --> 00:25:15,540
Your birth mother.

617
00:25:16,460 --> 00:25:17,060
Maybe.

618
00:25:18,060 --> 00:25:19,860
He hasn't been able to forget her
all these years?

619
00:25:20,620 --> 00:25:21,540
She must be really great then.

620
00:25:22,500 --> 00:25:23,500
I don't know.

621
00:25:23,820 --> 00:25:25,460
I don't even know what she looks like.

622
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:36,400
[Feng Rui]

623
00:25:43,820 --> 00:25:45,060
I'll get straight to the point then.

624
00:25:46,100 --> 00:25:47,140
I'm not here today

625
00:25:47,140 --> 00:25:48,380
to blame you.

626
00:25:49,060 --> 00:25:50,580
I just want to ask you a few questions.

627
00:25:52,100 --> 00:25:53,020
Of course, no pressure.

628
00:25:53,620 --> 00:25:54,980
If you don't want to answer,

629
00:25:55,700 --> 00:25:56,500
you don't have to.

630
00:25:57,820 --> 00:25:58,380
No problem.

631
00:25:59,060 --> 00:26:00,060
I'll tell you

632
00:26:00,060 --> 00:26:00,740
whatever I know.

633
00:26:04,500 --> 00:26:07,340
When did you and Feng Rui get together?

634
00:26:09,860 --> 00:26:11,100
This time, it was

635
00:26:11,100 --> 00:26:13,140
when we went
to Hongyuan County in Sichuan.

636
00:26:18,220 --> 00:26:19,460
In the years I've known Feng Rui,

637
00:26:19,580 --> 00:26:20,580
I've always known

638
00:26:21,260 --> 00:26:22,940
he carried Le's mom in his heart.

639
00:26:23,580 --> 00:26:24,740
But I didn't know

640
00:26:25,700 --> 00:26:26,980
Le's mom is still alive,

641
00:26:27,820 --> 00:26:28,580
and that it is you.

642
00:26:29,500 --> 00:26:31,220
Otherwise,
I wouldn't have naively tried to

643
00:26:31,580 --> 00:26:32,820
start this relationship.

644
00:26:34,980 --> 00:26:36,220
So I want to know

645
00:26:36,940 --> 00:26:38,740
what exactly happened between you.

646
00:26:39,580 --> 00:26:40,380
Why did you

647
00:26:40,380 --> 00:26:42,300
leave Le and Feng Rui,

648
00:26:42,940 --> 00:26:44,420
and why have you come back now?

649
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:47,500
I don't want to bow out
without knowing the reasons.

650
00:26:50,780 --> 00:26:51,300
Okay.

651
00:26:56,100 --> 00:26:56,420
Welcome...

652
00:26:57,420 --> 00:26:58,060
Ms. Gao?

653
00:27:03,780 --> 00:27:04,620
Where's Feng Rui?

654
00:27:06,180 --> 00:27:06,900
Where did he go?

655
00:27:07,660 --> 00:27:08,660
I called him,

656
00:27:08,820 --> 00:27:09,540
but he didn't answer.

657
00:27:10,340 --> 00:27:11,340
Mr. Feng isn't here.

658
00:27:11,820 --> 00:27:12,620
We don't know either.

659
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:15,420
What do you mean you don't know?

660
00:27:16,220 --> 00:27:17,580
He hasn't been here
for the last couple of days.

661
00:27:17,820 --> 00:27:19,660
Said he's going to France
to expand the market.

662
00:27:20,100 --> 00:27:21,180
He's probably preparing

663
00:27:21,180 --> 00:27:22,140
for that lately.

664
00:27:23,620 --> 00:27:24,660
You didn't know?

665
00:27:25,420 --> 00:27:26,420
The French market?

666
00:27:33,740 --> 00:27:34,660
Gao Haotian?

667
00:27:35,780 --> 00:27:36,860
I never knew

668
00:27:37,420 --> 00:27:38,340
Feng Rui had an uncle.

669
00:27:40,340 --> 00:27:41,580
Gao Hui would never admit

670
00:27:41,860 --> 00:27:43,540
that she had a brother who was a rapist.

671
00:27:45,340 --> 00:27:46,660
So you got close to me

672
00:27:46,780 --> 00:27:47,740
to get back at her?

673
00:27:51,020 --> 00:27:52,100
Partly.

674
00:27:52,780 --> 00:27:53,780
But not entirely.

675
00:27:55,500 --> 00:27:56,780
But I must admit,

676
00:27:57,420 --> 00:27:59,780
I did use your relationship

677
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:02,500
to find out everything

678
00:28:02,500 --> 00:28:03,980
I wanted to know.

679
00:28:04,780 --> 00:28:05,740
I'm really sorry.

680
00:28:08,260 --> 00:28:09,260
Having said that,

681
00:28:10,540 --> 00:28:12,180
I'm grateful to you.

682
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:14,020
All these years,

683
00:28:14,580 --> 00:28:15,540
you've been there for Le,

684
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:16,620
taking care of him,

685
00:28:17,340 --> 00:28:19,020
making up for the fact
that he didn't have a mom.

686
00:28:19,860 --> 00:28:21,260
You don't need to thank me, actually.

687
00:28:22,340 --> 00:28:24,820
It's not entirely because of Feng Rui
that I'm good to Le.

688
00:28:25,540 --> 00:28:27,740
Le really is a lovely child.

689
00:28:29,780 --> 00:28:30,940
And perhaps

690
00:28:31,460 --> 00:28:32,180
whom we meet in this world,

691
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:34,180
when we meet them,

692
00:28:35,100 --> 00:28:36,540
and what kind of relationship we form,

693
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:39,100
are all predestined.

694
00:28:44,260 --> 00:28:45,700
I've been thinking a lot lately.

695
00:28:45,700 --> 00:28:47,980
There were some things
I couldn't figure out.

696
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:50,260
Now I've finally figured it out.

697
00:28:52,220 --> 00:28:52,940
It's all in the past now.

698
00:28:57,340 --> 00:28:58,500
And I hope he finds happiness.

699
00:29:18,580 --> 00:29:19,300
Are you okay?

700
00:29:20,180 --> 00:29:21,180
Why wouldn't I be?

701
00:29:22,300 --> 00:29:23,780
You didn't answer my calls.

702
00:29:25,420 --> 00:29:26,700
Peiyan came to see me.

703
00:29:30,620 --> 00:29:31,860
What did she say?

704
00:29:32,620 --> 00:29:33,900
She said a lot of bad things about you.

705
00:29:36,980 --> 00:29:37,980
Just kidding.

706
00:29:41,700 --> 00:29:42,580
She wanted to know why.

707
00:29:42,580 --> 00:29:44,180
So I told her everything.

708
00:29:45,700 --> 00:29:47,300
I thought she had the right

709
00:29:47,500 --> 00:29:48,140
to know.

710
00:29:51,220 --> 00:29:51,620
I'm hanging up.

711
00:29:52,180 --> 00:29:52,580
Bye.

712
00:30:08,060 --> 00:30:08,500
Dad.

713
00:30:09,620 --> 00:30:10,820
Did you break up with Ms. Wen

714
00:30:10,820 --> 00:30:12,580
because you're still thinking
about my mom?

715
00:30:16,540 --> 00:30:17,340
It's nothing.

716
00:30:17,820 --> 00:30:18,740
I was just asking.

717
00:30:27,460 --> 00:30:27,780
Le,

718
00:30:28,820 --> 00:30:30,020
do you want to go on a trip?

719
00:30:30,780 --> 00:30:31,260
Yes.

720
00:30:31,820 --> 00:30:32,260
Where to?

721
00:30:33,980 --> 00:30:34,380
Abroad.

722
00:30:35,340 --> 00:30:35,740
With who?

723
00:30:37,540 --> 00:30:38,460
With me, of course.

724
00:30:39,980 --> 00:30:40,940
Just the two of us?

725
00:30:43,420 --> 00:30:43,820
You don't want to?

726
00:30:44,860 --> 00:30:45,220
Alright.

727
00:30:45,860 --> 00:30:46,740
Which country?

728
00:30:47,500 --> 00:30:48,700
France. How about that?

729
00:30:49,180 --> 00:30:49,980
France?

730
00:30:50,660 --> 00:30:52,540
Just the two of us guys going to France?

731
00:30:55,060 --> 00:30:56,220
But whatever.

732
00:30:57,060 --> 00:30:58,780
As long as we're having fun,
anywhere is fine.

733
00:30:59,820 --> 00:31:00,420
How long for?

734
00:31:01,340 --> 00:31:02,140
How long do you want to go for?

735
00:31:02,580 --> 00:31:03,860
The longer, the better.

736
00:31:07,660 --> 00:31:08,580
But Grandma

737
00:31:08,580 --> 00:31:10,260
told me to focus on studying recently.

738
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:13,260
True.

739
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:16,060
You need to behave well.

740
00:31:17,500 --> 00:31:18,740
Like you need to tell me that.

741
00:31:34,540 --> 00:31:35,540
I had to

742
00:31:36,420 --> 00:31:37,980
come to the school to see you.

743
00:31:42,660 --> 00:31:44,940
I didn't mean to ignore your calls.

744
00:31:45,300 --> 00:31:46,060
I just

745
00:31:47,060 --> 00:31:48,220
didn't know what to say.

746
00:31:50,940 --> 00:31:52,460
I didn't expect things
to turn out like this.

747
00:31:55,140 --> 00:31:56,420
I'm sorry, Yan.

748
00:31:57,380 --> 00:31:57,860
Madam,

749
00:31:58,740 --> 00:32:00,140
you don't need to apologize to me.

750
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:02,660
Matters of the heart

751
00:32:03,660 --> 00:32:04,820
are hard to explain.

752
00:32:07,620 --> 00:32:08,740
You're a good girl.

753
00:32:09,500 --> 00:32:10,580
And you're good to Le.

754
00:32:11,020 --> 00:32:12,140
I've seen it all.

755
00:32:13,420 --> 00:32:14,820
When I found out you two were together,

756
00:32:15,260 --> 00:32:16,260
I was really happy for you.

757
00:32:17,500 --> 00:32:18,700
You're not getting any younger.

758
00:32:19,940 --> 00:32:21,140
I hope you can

759
00:32:22,100 --> 00:32:23,140
settle down soon.

760
00:32:27,380 --> 00:32:29,100
Tan Siting told me everything.

761
00:32:36,940 --> 00:32:37,940
What did she say?

762
00:32:41,540 --> 00:32:43,060
It doesn't matter what she said.

763
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:45,140
That's just her side of the story.

764
00:32:47,980 --> 00:32:49,100
I won't comment

765
00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:51,220
on what's between you.

766
00:32:52,100 --> 00:32:53,260
But now that I know

767
00:32:53,460 --> 00:32:54,900
Tan Siting is Le's mom,

768
00:32:56,020 --> 00:32:57,020
there's no way things could work out

769
00:32:58,580 --> 00:32:59,620
between me and Feng Rui.

770
00:32:59,980 --> 00:33:01,340
She just appeared

771
00:33:01,340 --> 00:33:03,100
in Rui's life before you did.

772
00:33:04,340 --> 00:33:05,420
But that's not important.

773
00:33:06,340 --> 00:33:07,700
They aren't right for each other.

774
00:33:08,220 --> 00:33:09,620
They're not meant to be.

775
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:12,220
I always felt like

776
00:33:12,980 --> 00:33:14,260
Rui was living

777
00:33:15,180 --> 00:33:16,740
inside a shell.

778
00:33:17,580 --> 00:33:18,780
I tried hard

779
00:33:18,780 --> 00:33:19,780
to break through it.

780
00:33:21,260 --> 00:33:22,140
But unfortunately,

781
00:33:23,460 --> 00:33:24,660
I never managed to get inside.

782
00:33:25,980 --> 00:33:26,540
Yan,

783
00:33:27,420 --> 00:33:28,300
if you love someone,

784
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:30,100
you should persevere.

785
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:30,860
Don't give up.

786
00:33:31,540 --> 00:33:32,660
I'll help you.

787
00:33:51,180 --> 00:33:52,260
I've been carrying

788
00:33:52,540 --> 00:33:53,660
this necklace with me lately.

789
00:33:54,460 --> 00:33:56,180
I wanted to find the right time
to return it to you.

790
00:33:57,420 --> 00:33:58,140
Today seems fitting.

791
00:34:02,140 --> 00:34:03,300
Thank you for looking out for me

792
00:34:04,540 --> 00:34:05,260
all this time.

793
00:34:24,900 --> 00:34:25,500
Okay.

794
00:34:26,420 --> 00:34:28,620
Alright. We're here.

795
00:34:28,900 --> 00:34:29,180
Hello, Mr. Lu.

796
00:34:29,180 --> 00:34:29,620
Le.

797
00:34:30,660 --> 00:34:31,100
Mr. Feng.

798
00:34:31,100 --> 00:34:31,500
Lu.

799
00:34:32,220 --> 00:34:32,820
I'll take it.

800
00:34:36,660 --> 00:34:37,820
Dad, aren't you coming home?

801
00:34:38,660 --> 00:34:39,420
I still have some things
to take care of.

802
00:34:39,780 --> 00:34:41,340
I'll come back as soon as I'm done.

803
00:34:41,660 --> 00:34:42,060
Okay.

804
00:34:42,220 --> 00:34:43,500
Alright. Go upstairs with Lu.

805
00:34:43,980 --> 00:34:44,780
Okay. Bye.

806
00:34:44,780 --> 00:34:45,060
Bye.

807
00:34:52,700 --> 00:34:53,740
Hello, Ms. Tan.

808
00:34:54,180 --> 00:34:55,700
Guess what my dad told me today?

809
00:34:56,020 --> 00:34:56,780
What did he say?

810
00:34:57,180 --> 00:34:58,580
He said if I behave well,

811
00:34:58,580 --> 00:34:59,980
he'll take me to France.

812
00:35:01,340 --> 00:35:01,900
Really?

813
00:35:02,580 --> 00:35:04,220
Then you better behave well.

814
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:06,020
Ms. Tan,

815
00:35:06,420 --> 00:35:08,420
I remember you used to
live in France, right?

816
00:35:08,900 --> 00:35:09,340
Yeah.

817
00:35:10,820 --> 00:35:12,780
Then you can be my remote tour guide.

818
00:35:13,140 --> 00:35:14,620
I want to see if French ballet

819
00:35:14,620 --> 00:35:15,700
is really as amazing as they say.

820
00:35:16,100 --> 00:35:17,380
Of course, no problem.

821
00:35:18,060 --> 00:35:18,860
Alright. Come eat.

822
00:35:23,580 --> 00:35:23,940
Hello?

823
00:35:24,580 --> 00:35:25,500
Who's at your house?

824
00:35:27,580 --> 00:35:29,340
Two of my colleagues came over
for dinner.

825
00:35:30,660 --> 00:35:31,900
Then you should eat.

826
00:35:32,940 --> 00:35:33,300
Le,

827
00:35:33,580 --> 00:35:35,220
can you give me your home address?

828
00:35:35,220 --> 00:35:36,580
I want to send you a gift.

829
00:35:37,180 --> 00:35:37,820
A gift?

830
00:35:39,700 --> 00:35:40,700
Thanks, Ms. Tan.

831
00:35:41,100 --> 00:35:42,140
No problem. I'm hanging up now.

832
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:42,820
Bye.

833
00:35:47,580 --> 00:35:48,140
He didn't hear, did he?

834
00:35:48,660 --> 00:35:50,220
I was so scared.

835
00:35:50,940 --> 00:35:51,900
He almost heard.

836
00:35:51,940 --> 00:35:52,900
Good thing he didn't
recognize your voice.

837
00:35:52,980 --> 00:35:54,740
Why did you ask for his address?

838
00:35:54,740 --> 00:35:55,660
You could have just asked me.

839
00:35:56,420 --> 00:35:57,940
Are you silly?

840
00:36:00,060 --> 00:36:00,380
Right.

841
00:36:01,260 --> 00:36:01,580
Right.

842
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:50,540
Is he asleep?

843
00:36:54,500 --> 00:36:55,220
You should just sleep here too.

844
00:36:55,740 --> 00:36:56,660
No need to go back and forth.

845
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:10,660
Your grandpa misses you.

846
00:37:11,420 --> 00:37:12,820
He wants you to come over
for dinner tomorrow.

847
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:16,380
I see.

848
00:37:30,580 --> 00:37:31,260
It's been a long time

849
00:37:32,420 --> 00:37:34,780
since our whole family
had a proper meal together.

850
00:37:35,860 --> 00:37:36,420
Rui,

851
00:37:37,540 --> 00:37:38,940
how is your winery doing?

852
00:37:40,660 --> 00:37:41,220
It's good.

853
00:37:41,660 --> 00:37:43,220
Cygne is on track now.

854
00:37:44,060 --> 00:37:44,860
Our vineyard

855
00:37:44,860 --> 00:37:46,380
is gradually increasing production.

856
00:37:46,780 --> 00:37:48,500
We've also seen
a significant growth in orders.

857
00:37:49,620 --> 00:37:50,620
You're doing very well.

858
00:37:51,940 --> 00:37:52,780
You always

859
00:37:53,580 --> 00:37:55,540
put my mind at ease
when it comes to work.

860
00:37:59,940 --> 00:38:00,540
Rui,

861
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:04,420
your mom

862
00:38:06,340 --> 00:38:07,540
told me about your situation.

863
00:38:08,540 --> 00:38:09,260
Young people

864
00:38:09,820 --> 00:38:12,260
tend to be impulsive
in matters of the heart.

865
00:38:13,060 --> 00:38:13,860
It's understandable.

866
00:38:15,060 --> 00:38:16,540
But the engagement thing

867
00:38:17,060 --> 00:38:18,540
is truly beyond repair now.

868
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:20,220
I understand.

869
00:38:21,820 --> 00:38:23,780
You have feelings for Ms. Tan.

870
00:38:25,540 --> 00:38:26,540
But your relationship

871
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:27,700
is too complicated.

872
00:38:28,420 --> 00:38:29,860
Ms. Tan is different from you.

873
00:38:30,420 --> 00:38:32,060
You're not just on your own.

874
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:33,700
You have a large family

875
00:38:34,340 --> 00:38:35,620
and a business

